data.description: Welcome to 1201 Muirfield Drive, Findlay, OH 45840! Step into this stately 2-story colonial home, where the journey begins with a grand entrance. Inside, you'll be captivated by the seamless open concept design that effortlessly flows from the Living room to formal dining room to the modern shaker-style kitchen that is adorned with granite counters, the kitchen serves as the heart of this home. A convenient drop zone and main floor laundry room make daily life a breeze. Your vehicles will find shelter in the 2-car attached garage, and ample storage throughout ensures an organized living space. Upstairs, the large primary bedroom offers comfort and privacy. As you step outside, you'll appreciate the charming brick exterior that adds character to the property, relax on the large open patio overlooking the 12th hole of Hillcrest Golf Club. This home combines timeless elegance with practicality, making it the perfect place to call your own.
